8042
<<Only for advanced Users:>>

Here, you can define the ZModem protocol options for
the Fido-Mailer. Normally, this field will be empty
and the Fido-Mailer will operate with the correct
parameters.

Possible options:

<<-r>>   Crash Recovery.

<<-ti>>  Timeout Duration .....

     The number of "inactive" seconds the protocol
     will wait before timing out. By default, it
     will wait 300 seconds (-t300) before timing
     out. This may need to be increased for File
     Requests, as some Mailers need to search
     through large filebases and therefore, need
