<<Re-Org / Messages

Deletes all messages which are scheduled for
deletion, either by being marked by you or because
they have reached the set time limit. The time is
measured from the <<"date received">>.

Note that extra disk space is needed during the
reorganisation. As a general rule; about one tenth of
the space used by CrossPoint in total. The more the
better.

The reorganisation can take a long time on a large
data base, but can be interrupted with <Esc>.
