These holes are gradually reused by new messages, but
in the event of a major clean-up deleting a lot of
messages, a lot of wasted space could exist for a
while. "Pack" eliminated this wasted space all at
once.

Packing is even slower than the message Re-Org, but
that should not be a problem, since it is seldom
needed.
