12101
<<Message / Forward / Copy

A <<COPY>> of the current message is forwarded to
either a User, a Newsgroup or sent "Direct". You can
select the recipient from either a list of
Newsgroups, a list of Users or choose to send the
message "Direct". The [Template/Forward] is used@10807
to indicate that the message has been copied. You
become the sender of the copy, replies to the copy
come to you and the original sender is noted in the
message header.

