@
12106
<<Message / Forward / Confirmation

The sender of the selected message is sent an
automatic message confirming your receipt of it.
It contains the following information:

þ Message-ID
þ Date and time of writing (of the original)
þ Size of the message received
þ The route the message took on its journey

