The zone numbers in FIDO are:

  <<1>>  North America      <<4>>  South America
  <<2>>  Europe             <<5>>  Africa
  <<3>>  Oceania            <<6>>  Asia

The European region numbers are:

<<20>> Sweden      <<30>> Switzerland <<40>> Israel
<<21>> Norway      <<31>> Austria     <<41>> Greece
<<22>> Finland     <<32>> France      <<42>> CSFR
<<23>> Denmark     <<33>> Italy       <<43>> Turkey
<<24>> Germany     <<34>> Spain       <<46>> Ukraine
<<25>> UK          <<35>> Bulgaria    <<47>> Lithuania
<<26>> Eire        <<36>> Portugal    <<48>> Poland
